{"tid":817087,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海航系再爆3億違約 現負債逾5000億人幣","createTime":"2018-09-13T07:11:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T11:58:44.000Z","uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0561eb460a2b7f05478a8fe8c0257fb3485b8d66","tid":817087,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T07:11:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.ft.com/__origami/service/image/v2/images/raw/http%3A%2F%2Fi.ftimg.net%2Fpicture%2F9%2F000069439_piclink.jpg?source=ftchinese&amp;width=670&amp;height=377&amp;fit=cover&amp;from=next001\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2F__origami%2Fservice%2Fimage%2Fv2%2Fimages%2Fraw%2Fhttp%253A%252F%252Fi.ftimg.net%252Fpicture%252F9%252F000069439_piclink.jpg%3Fsource%3Dftchinese%26width%3D670%26height%3D377%26fit%3Dcover%26from%3Dnext001&h=c22b1ffa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n湖南省信託周四公告稱，海航集團子公司海航創新一筆3億元（人民幣．下同）的信託計畫貸款本金，應於9月10日前歸還，但是截至公告發出前，尚未收到相關款項，因此構成實質違約。湖南信託已委派專門人員前往現場催收，督促其盡快還款，並擬凍結其及借款擔保人的資產。<br />\n<br />\n公告顯示，上述信託計劃於2016年9月8日成立，資金用於向海航創新發放流動資金貸款，貸款規模3億元人民幣，貸款期限24個月，由海航旅遊集團有限公司為該項貸款提供連帶責任保證擔保。<br />\n<br />\n從今年起，海航已經出售了超過170億美元的資產，但總負債和融資成本仍然高企。近期海航集團稱計畫退出在德意志銀行的全部股份，為貨櫃租賃業務Seaco尋求買家，並放棄香港中環一處從未使用的辦公空間。<br />\n<br />\n本報今日報道，據市場消息人士透露，海航將放棄租用中環交易廣場三期共8層寫字樓，現正在市場低調放租有關樓面，當中一層24樓以上單數層成功租出，另有3層正有企業洽租中，租金相對海航集團承租時每方呎140元為高。<br />\n<br />\n該8層樓面分佈在24至31樓，涉及樓面約9萬餘方呎，每層約11,000餘方呎，每方呎租金叫價約180元。據悉，交易廣場三期大業主置地亦知悉海航在市場尋求新租戶頂租該批樓面。而置地亦作兩手準備，若未有新租戶，不排除會追討海航違約。<br />\n<br />\n截至6月底，海航集團的債務總額下降9.5%至5,416億元人民幣，較去年年底減少逾80億美元。但從總負債規模來看，海航仍然是亞洲地區負債規模最大的非金融企業之一。"},{"pid":"97e78d8b5a653c1b8178338bc53501bc350d8be2","tid":817087,"uid":30169,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T07:12:16.000Z","msg":"垃圾公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"530b9c1ee6739f1c755ec3e16c65d684e5c92460","tid":817087,"uid":39365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T07:16:37.000Z","msg":"其實就算賣晒所有資產, 都清唔到5000億負債"},{"pid":"46c36e2ee861b6c3e0281a7af38f57477697e905","tid":817087,"uid":48973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T07:18:08.000Z","msg":"用支付寶比咪得囉"},{"pid":"068d49dafb0071e4f95f4a0ce5d57647666652b2","tid":817087,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T07:24:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大驚少怪！！！&quot;債轉估&quot;咪冇事囉！！！</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc8493481d9dbdaf44e6a5f73f7d995b4790acd","tid":817087,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T07:25:25.000Z","msg":"5000億<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n誠哥枱面身家幾多話？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a90e432331597de5e9d2b343ecfb89e81400cd25","tid":817087,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T10:31:00.000Z","msg":"沒事兒 咱們喝兩杯"},{"pid":"a0d76ca11bf7fec39fab19e7c7b70c49f211e029","tid":817087,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"068d49dafb0071e4f95f4a0ce5d57647666652b2","tid":817087,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T07:24:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大驚少怪！！！&quot;債轉估&quot;咪冇事囉！！！</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T11:53:22.000Z","msg":"5000億，齋鑽股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都搞唔掂"},{"pid":"1df0f9a82450e77f36c75528caf38ff42c690c0e","tid":817087,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T11:58:44.000Z","msg":"冰冰啲錢係咪拎左去幫海航還債<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" c